A Nigerian man identified as Justice Ondaipe and his wife has welcomed a beautiful set of twins after 21 years of marriage. A family member, Faith Elvis Ovie shared the good news on Saturday, June 12, said Ondaipe’s wife gave birth to a boy and a girl. READ ALSO: Oyo commence evacuation of beggars to Akinyele resettlement centre “Congratulations uncle, God is indeed wonderful. After 21 years of marriage, God has put a smile on ur face. God even doubled it. Twins, a boy, and a girl.”